This paper discusses the use of RDF triples and reasoning mechanisms, which are commonly studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the performance of reasoning processes on RDF datasets, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
